      <title>盈利季面临重大考验：零售商的节日前景</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/earnings-season-faces-major-test-retailers-holiday-outlooks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[上周的抛售就发生在美国企业普遍成功的财报季之后，投资者正准备迎接最后一个考验：未来几天将公布的一系列零售业领头羊的零售业报告，以了解消费者的消费状况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/earnings-season-faces-major-test-retailers-holiday-outlooks</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国农民动员阻止欧盟南方共同市场贸易协定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/french-farmers-mobilize-to-block-eu-s-mercosur-trade-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国强大的农业工会再次走上街头寻求更多的政府支持，并反对欧盟与拉丁美洲生产商达成的允许更廉价商品的自由贸易协定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/french-farmers-mobilize-to-block-eu-s-mercosur-trade-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 09:58:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Raiffeisen 提出与俄罗斯合作，但 3 月份取消了与 AT1 的交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/raiffeisen-starts-at1-sale-after-failed-deal-over-russia-link</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于难以退出俄罗斯业务，奥里夫森银行国际股份公司 (Raiffeisen Bank International AG) 的一笔交易失败，目前该行正试图筹集新资本，以取代额外一级债券。六个多月前，该行曾发行过一笔额外一级债券，但最终以失败告终。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/raiffeisen-starts-at1-sale-after-failed-deal-over-russia-link</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 09:52:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非莱利银行计划斥资 6.62 亿美元进军非洲市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/nedbank-plots-expansion-into-africa-with-662-million-war-chest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非莱利银行集团有限公司 (Nedbank Group Ltd.) 正着手重塑非洲大陆，希望减少对南非的依赖，并在未来十年内将其从其他非洲市场获得的利润增加近四倍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/nedbank-plots-expansion-into-africa-with-662-million-war-chest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 09:28:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ICE 欧洲期货交易所总裁对联合债务发行“充满信心”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/ice-futures-europe-president-on-eu-bond-futures-launch-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[ICE Futures Europe 总裁 Christopher Rhodes 表示，尽管发行计划存在“不确定性”，但欧盟债券将在 2026 年以后发挥作用。该公司计划下个月推出与欧盟债务指数挂钩的期货合约。Rhodes 在“彭博：开盘交易”节目中与 Kriti Gupta、Guy Johnson 和 Anna Edwards 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-11-18/ice-futures-europe-president-on-eu-bond-futures-launch-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 09:21:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ICE 表示，尽管存在发行疑虑，但欧盟债券期货仍将取得成功</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/eu-bond-futures-can-succeed-despite-issuance-doubts-says-ice</link>
      <description><![CDATA[洲际交易所一位高管表示，欧盟债券将在未来几年继续在市场上发挥重要作用，这驳斥了人们对欧盟作为主要发行国的长期地位的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/eu-bond-futures-can-succeed-despite-issuance-doubts-says-ice</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 08:31:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲股市下跌，因交易员权衡特朗普政策和中国</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/european-stocks-pause-as-traders-weigh-trump-policies-china</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对唐纳德·特朗普政策的担忧以及中国股市未能守住盘中涨幅，欧洲股市周一小幅走低。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/european-stocks-pause-as-traders-weigh-trump-policies-china</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 08:28:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国控制出口举措扰乱铝库存和价格</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/china-s-bid-to-rein-in-exports-roils-aluminum-stocks-and-prices</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国取消出口减税措施后，铝行业忙于评估其对供应流造成的影响，中国铝业公司的股价大幅下跌，而国际铝业公司的股价则出现上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/china-s-bid-to-rein-in-exports-roils-aluminum-stocks-and-prices</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 05:20:45 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>高盛重申 2025 年 3,000 美元的目标，黄金价格反弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/gold-rebounds-after-deep-weekly-loss-with-rate-outlook-in-flux</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美元小幅走低且考虑到唐纳德·特朗普明年重返白宫，交易员权衡美联储降息前景，金价在创下 2021 年以来最大周跌幅后上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-18/gold-rebounds-after-deep-weekly-loss-with-rate-outlook-in-flux</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 18 Nov 2024 01:19:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普团队正寻求放宽美国自动驾驶汽车规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/trump-team-said-to-want-to-ease-us-rules-for-self-driving-cars</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，当选总统唐纳德·特朗普的过渡团队成员告诉顾问，他们计划将完全自动驾驶汽车的联邦框架作为交通部的优先事项之一。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-17/trump-team-said-to-want-to-ease-us-rules-for-self-driving-cars</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 17 Nov 2024 20:43:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
